reviewText: A touching story of complex situations and different ways of relating and understanding. We hope for happiness and a fulfillment for the two main characters.
DIRECT HIT TO MY HEART AND WHAT IS GOING ON IN MY LIFE.
Good story.. it is no summer blockbuster but then again, I hate CGI

This movie was OK. In many ways it was very accurate.
Watch Adam. Or Mary and Max. Those are excellent movies to learn about Asperger's, in my opinion.
